task.summary: Lanternfish Resources + GeckoLib integration + Crabs + L + Ratio
Crab bucket, proper spawn egg, behavior, breeding/tempting
Fixed Crab Bucket, and made Crabs bucketable
Cleaned up Item registry
Updated animations
Dyeable crabs
Blue crab is default
Loot table change + final crab features (for now)
Start of Crab Claw (not finished - really tricky)
Updated Crab Barrel Texture and added crab drop
Add spawn egg to creative tab and fix crab spawning event
Fix z-fighting on crab trap model & finalized crab spawning
Re-wrote crab trap loot handler
Crab Trap methods for chum nearly done
Fixed Crab Trap chum logic to replace the bucket; Thank you MehVahdJukaar!
Created chum bucket recipes and associated tags; re-generated data
Increment Version for 1.20.1 release
Merged the ja_jp translation - added in the missing items related to items added in this latest update to default to the en_us translation until new translations are received
Add ru_ru.json - thanks Maxis!
Finally fixed the bowl returning issue
Incremented version to 1.1.3a for hotfix
JEI stubs and Item Tooltips
Bump 1.1.4
Pufferfish slices
Adjust crab cakes recipe
Fix for fish barrels not dropping when broken
Fixed fishing loot table to (hopefully) not be overwritten entirely; Refactored loot table structure for crab trap loot; Updated dependency on Farmer's Delight to latest version
Reduced crab spawn weight; Added Shrimp Fried Rice; Assets for Arid and Soggy fleshes; Removed JEI plugin until I can figure it out
Fixed Shrimp Fried Rice category; Temporarily removed Lanternfish Barrels
Temporarily removed Lanternfish Barrels; Added Achievement related to a new dish; THE CLAW
Arid and Soggy Flesh
Crab Claw 2D and 3D Models
Crab claw properly takes damage - verified enchantability and durability work as intended
Mild changes to crab claw - added to loot table for crabs - fixed crabs dropping multiple raw crabs on death - added Jar of Pickles and Sea Pickle Juice
Fixed crab drop mistake - increment mod version to 1.1.5
I think the loot table is finally fixed - proper recipes for pickle dishes - removed weakness and added a brief nausea to sea pickle juice
Inky Potion and Sea Pickle Juice recipe change
Inky Potion Recipe not working yet :(
Inky potion recipe finished with access transformer - temporarily removed arid and soggy flesh
Removed the soggy and arid flesh recipes - reworked how tags are added - restarted JEI integration but it no work yet
Fixed issues with Crab Claw - updated zh_cn translation - increment mod version
Added Squid Tentacles and Frog Legs
Remade Crab Leg Texture
Increase Chum durability to 48 - Modify Crab Trap to have 27 slots - Stub for Renderer for Items inside of Crab Trap
Created .gitignore
